  <brief_title>To Evaluate Efficacy and Safety of Z-215 in Erosive Esophagitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Multicenter Study to Evaluate Efficacy and Safety of Z-215 Compared With Rabeprazole Sodium in the Treatment of Erosive Esophagitis</official_title>
