  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy and safety of Z-215 (10 mg, 20 mg, 40
      mg) , compared with Rabeprazole Sodium 10mg in patients with erosive esophagitis of Grade A
      to D as defined by the LA classification grading system.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
